data.title: 15 Wakefield Avenue, Withers WA 6230
data.meta_description: View this 4 bedroom, 1 bathroom house for sale at 15 Wakefield Avenue, Withers. See 24 photos, Withers statistics, agent details & more.
data.text:
This home is perfect for those entering the property market, seeking an investment opportunity or looking to downsize close to the ocean.

This 4 bedroom home comes complete with an underground pool, perfect to keep cool on long hot summer days. With most of its original décor, the interior boasts wooden look flooring and an extension built on for extra room, the kitchen is the heart of the home with open plan style dining area with room for the whole family.

Situated close to the ocean, walking distance to Maidens Reserve, close to shops, schools and amenities. Get in quick, it won't last long.

For more information or to arrange a private viewing, call exclusive selling agent Tim Cooper today!

PROPERTY FEATURES YOU'LL LOVE

Master bedroom with walk in robe

Three minor bedrooms

One bathroom

Well-appointed kitchen with ample storage

Open plan dining room with wood fire

Separate lounge with wood look flooring

Extension for extra family room

Exposed ceiling beams

Below ground pool

Patio area for entertaining

Garden Shed

Established garden beds and lawn

Single lock up garage

Walking distance to the beach

LOCATION FEATURES NEARBY

Maidens Reserve – 1.3km

Maidens Primary School – 700m

Newton Moore High School – 1.4km

Beach – 1km

Bunbury CBD – 5.9km

Built: 1974

Land size: 690m2

Land rates: $2401.88 approx. P/YR

Water rates: $251.89 approx. P/YR

* Rental appraisal: After careful consideration of the current rental market, we believe that the above property could attain a rental return of $520-$570 per week. Please note this is not a sworn evaluation and the price is subject to change with market conditions and rental demand at the time of marketing.

Are you interested in buying, renting or investing in Withers? Here at REIWA, we recognise that choosing the right suburb is not an easy choice.

To provide an understanding of the kind of lifestyle Withers offers, we've collated all the relevant market information, key facts, demographics and statistics to help you make a confident and informed decision.

Our interactive map allows you to delve deeper into this suburb and locate points of interest like transport, schools and amenities.
